  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要画一个云原生Docker镜像处理的状态机。整个流程从K8s集群触发，经过IDLE、FETCH、PARSE这几个阶段，然后根据解析结果分流到ARB_READ或者ERROR。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "CloudNative_K8sCluster",
        "IDLE",
        "FETCH",
        "PARSE",
        "ARB_READ",
        "ERROR"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白，PARSE之后Valid走ARB_READ，Invalid走ERROR。那ARB_READ到READ的触发条件是什么？还有READ之后的流向呢？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "PARSE",
        "ARB_READ",
        "ERROR",
        "READ"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "ARB_READ收到Grant信号后进入READ，READ完成会走到ARB_WRITE，同样Grant之后进入WRITE。WRITE完成再到CHAIN状态，这里有个循环逻辑——CHAIN如果不是最后一条，就Next回到FETCH继续处理；如果是Last，就到COMPLETE。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "ARB_READ",
        "READ",
        "ARB_WRITE",
        "WRITE",
        "CHAIN",
        "FETCH",
        "COMPLETE"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我先把主干状态都画出来，从K8sCluster到IDLE，然后FETCH、PARSE、ARB_READ、READ、ARB_WRITE、WRITE、CHAIN，最后COMPLETE。边和触发条件我标注一下Kick-off、Complete这些。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "CloudNative_K8sCluster",
        "IDLE",
        "FETCH",
        "PARSE",
        "ARB_READ",
        "READ",
        "ARB_WRITE",
        "WRITE",
        "CHAIN",
        "COMPLETE"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "主干看起来对。不过COMPLETE之后应该有个中断机制回到IDLE，ERROR状态也需要能软件清除回到IDLE，这两个收尾别忘了。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "COMPLETE",
        "ERROR",
        "IDLE"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "加上了，COMPLETE到IDLE是IRQ sent，ERROR到IDLE是SW clear。另外我检查了一下，CHAIN到FETCH的触发条件应该是Next，到COMPLETE是Last，对吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "CHAIN",
        "FETCH",
        "COMPLETE",
        "IDLE",
        "ERROR"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "repair",
      "utterance": "CHAIN到FETCH的触发条件表述需要调整一下，不是'Next'，应该是'Kick-off'那种风格的动作描述，用'Next'容易产生歧义。等等，不对，我再看一下——CHAIN到FETCH确实是'Next'，但PARSE到ARB_READ的条件我刚才说的是Valid，你写的是Complete？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "CHAIN",
        "FETCH",
        "PARSE",
        "ARB_READ"
      ],
      "is_repair": true
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "repair",
      "utterance": "收到，我修正一下：PARSE到ARB_READ是Valid，PARSE到ERROR是Invalid。FETCH到PARSE才是Complete。CHAIN到FETCH保持Next，到COMPLETE是Last。现在所有边都核对过了。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "PARSE",
        "ARB_READ",
        "ERROR",
        "FETCH",
        "CHAIN",
        "COMPLETE"
      ],
      "is_repair": true
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 9,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "没问题了，整个状态机完整了。从K8s集群启动，经过完整的仲裁读写流程，支持链式批量处理，错误可恢复，最后中断复位。可以定稿了。",
